dct_description_sm: From Swedish and Russian charts ; Carrington, Hyd: Off: ; Published at the Admiralty, 26th, Sepr. 1874, under the Superintendence of Captain F. J. Evans, R.N. C.B. F.R.S. Hydrographer ; Sold by J. D. Potter, Agent for the sale of the Admiralty Charts, 145 Minories ; Engraved by Edwd. Weller.
Hachure relief with depths shown by soundings.
Shows various buoys, lights, coasts, small islands and rocks, railways, low water areas, waterways.
